================================================================================
                         SAMPLE CALCULATION
================================================================================

GIVEN:
  Salary 15th:    PHP 30,000.00
  Salary 30th:    PHP 30,000.00
  Overtime Hours: 5

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EARNINGS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Base monthly
  30000 + 30000 = 60,000.00

Total work hours/month
  22 × 8 = 176

Hourly rate
  60000 ÷ 176 = 340.909090...

Overtime pay
  340.909090... × 5 × 1.10 = 1,875.00

Bonus (15%)
  60000 × 0.15 = 9,000.00

Gross earnings
  60000 + 1875 + 9000 = 70,875.00

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEDUCTIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

SSS (4.5%)
  60000 × 0.045 = 2,700.00

PhilHealth (2.5%)
  60000 × 0.025 = 1,500.00

Pag-IBIG (2%)
  60000 × 0.02 = 1,200.00

Taxable income (for tax computation)
  70875 - 2700 - 1500 - 1200 = 65,475.00

Income Tax (2026, max 30% - Monthly)
  Monthly taxable = 65,475.00
  Since 65,475 is between 33,333 and 66,667 → 20% bracket
  Tax = 1,875 + (65,475 - 33,333) × 0.20
  Tax = 1,875 + 32,142 × 0.20
  Tax = 1,875 + 6,428.40
  Income tax = PHP 8,303.40

Total deductions
  2700 + 1500 + 1200 + 8303.40 = 13,703.40

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
NET PAY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Net pay
  70875 - 13703.40 = 57,171.60

================================================================================
                           FINAL ANSWERS
================================================================================

  Overtime         = PHP   1,875.00
  Bonus            = PHP   9,000.00
  Gross            = PHP  70,875.00
  Income Tax       = PHP   8,303.40
  Total Deductions = PHP  13,703.40
  Net Pay          = PHP  57,171.60

